title: Jerry Garcia & Howard Wales (1971) Hooteroll +2 [CD-FLAC]
description:
Hooteroll? + 2
Howard Wales and Jerry Garcia

[CD-FLAC] via EAC (log, cue)

LP release: 1971
CD release : 2010

A CD release of Hooteroll? that includes all tracks from the original LP (for the first time on CD) plus the additional tracks that were included on previous CD releases plus two previously unreleased bonus tracks. The live bonus tracks were recorded at the January 28, 1972 Garcia/Wales show in Providence, Rhode Island.

Tracks
01 Morning In Marin (Wales)
02 Da Birg Song (Wales)
03 South Side Strut (Fierro / Wales)
04 Up From The Desert (Wales)
05 A Trip To What Next (Wales)
06 DC-502 (Wales)
07 One A.M. Approach (Wales)
08 Uncle Martin's (Wales)
09 Evening In Marin (Wales)
10 She Once Lived Here (Inman)
11 Sweet Cocaine (Traditional)

Musicians
* Howard Wales - piano, organ
* Jerry Garcia - guitar
* John Kahn - bass
* Curly Cook - rhythm guitar
* Bill Vitt - drums
* Michael Marinelli - drums
* Ken Balzall - trumpet
* Martin Fierro - saxophone, flute
